I am from Amritsar Punjab and live in UK now , Lahore only 30 km away , yet two cultures so similar but yet unique , music and sports seems to be the only thing that brings us closer , especially music and this kind of music , I am sure even if one doesn't understand the words , this is so beautiful , words don't do justice , well done Atif , love to Pakistan from India and UK :) hope to visit soon places where our grandfathers lived. Gursimran Singh
